MESSAGE.value: Add support for binning variables and histogram.
Provide a means to change the theme of charts. Theme must be chosen before binding the variable to the plot.
Add bar chart and intention on Chart to refresh chart content. Useful when styles are changed that cannot be set on the component.
Move the construction of the chart to the style concept.
Add the ability to generate executable Java code that displays a frame with a bar chart when given a TSV file.
Add build script to create MPS plugin. This one was particularly tricky to build as the wizard failed to collect all dependencies.
Move Jar file directly under the XChart language. Hopefully will help find the jar with the plugin. Remove the lib and helper solutions.
Closing the chart should only dispose the chart, not close the JVM.
Increment version number. Provide vendor info.
Now use a custom swing wrapper that does not exit the JVM when the frame is closed.
Support customization of minX and maxY, as well as legend position.
Correctly generate legend positioning code and minY, maxY.
Support for multiple charts in a frame. Fix histograms generation.
Add missing files to git. Specify idea version in plugin.
Enter project description in language plugin.
Charts must not be rootable because they require a parent page to find the TSV and columns. Increment plugin version to 1.0.7.
Remove dependency on multiline and richtext projects.

Make ColumnLoader more robust to NaN in the values. Expose a method on CustomSwingWrapper that makes a JPanel with the charts. Useful to include the charts directly in a $swing component$ inside an MPS editor.

Replace NaNs with zero because the XChart library has trouble with those:
java.lang.NumberFormatException at java.math.BigDecimal.<init>(BigDecimal.java:459) at java.math.BigDecimal.<init>(BigDecimal.java:728) at java.math.BigDecimal.valueOf(BigDecimal.java:1054) at com.xeiam.xchart.internal.chartpart.AxisTickBarChartCalculator.calculate(AxisTickBarChartCalculator.java:122) at com.xeiam.xchart.internal.chartpart.AxisTickBarChartCalculator.<init>(AxisTickBarChartCalculator.java:48) at com.xeiam.xchart.internal.chartpart.AxisTick.paint(AxisTick.java:77) at com.xeiam.xchart.internal.chartpart.Axis.paint(Axis.java:240) at com.xeiam.xchart.internal.chartpart.AxisPair.paint(AxisPair.java:147) at com.xeiam.xchart.internal.chartpart.ChartPainter.paint(ChartPainter.java:110) at com.xeiam.xchart.internal.chartpart.ChartPainter.paint(ChartPainter.java:70) at com.xeiam.xchart.Chart.paint(Chart.java:94) at com.xeiam.xchart.XChartPanel.paintComponent(XChartPanel.java:89)
Increase version number and rebuild.
handle NaNs better.
Set the plugin version in the build script. Add git commit and build number to the POM.
Create build to commit history.
Set the plugin version in the build script (previous attempt did not work).
Add which branch was built in the builds-to-commits history.
